{"tid":1244740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【團結】連登仔成日話唔要大台，但自己就想成為大台","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:29:44.000Z","uid":37528,"like":68,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b183701ab9c08b94add976737dd70748bfd65db1","tid":1244740,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"講真，今次民陣都算係咁，同大家都算有商量，最緊要係唔割蓆，佢地都話要取消暴動呢個定性<br />\n但係某d連登仔就想民陣咩都聽佢地講。但兩邊支持者不嬲都唔係同一班人，邊有可能咩行動都一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山，勿分化&lt;--呢個係雙向<br />\n民陣唔割我地蓆同時，我地都唔應該有咩唔同意就同佢地割蓆<br />\n如果唔係咩叫各有各做<br />\n<br />\n利申：非泛民打手，以前屌左佢地好耐。但今次想贏港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b655c8d5f1ee89f9bd9ab2e60b43bf4d6d8b34","tid":1244740,"uid":37528,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"妥協係一人讓一步，唔係人讓一步，我地就行前一步<br />\n兩派各有可取架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9e1c547f6b3fb79798160efc493ce99dea7925","tid":1244740,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20347a71d04b875d2cd3dc44e932121780c5135f","tid":1244740,"uid":246380,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"有撚割過佢地蓆？<br />\n又用和平，民意呢啲字眼騎劫本土個班和理非最撚該死"},{"pid":"625bf1459860c45a5e3d04f42943958297652dcd","tid":1244740,"uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"20347a71d04b875d2cd3dc44e932121780c5135f","tid":1244740,"uid":246380,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"有撚割過佢地蓆？<br />\n又用和平，民意呢啲字眼騎劫本土個班和理非最撚該死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"理性少少啦<br />\n合作先有得贏"},{"pid":"1165cf17ab167df24a9